==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Willingness
<hw>Will"ing*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality or state of being
willing; free choice or consent of the will; freedom from reluctance;
readiness of the mind to do or forbear.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Sweet is the love which comes with <qex>willingness</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Dryden.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

